title: Eating Disorders Sourcebook -Judd- PDF [Slender]
description:
Publisher: Omnigraphics Inc; 3 edition (November 2010)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 0780811437
ISBN-13: 978-0780811430

Basic consumer health information about Anorexia Nervosa, Bulimia, Binge Eating, Compulsive Exercise, Female Athlete Triad, and other eating disorders, including facts about body image and other cultural and age-related risk factors, prevention efforts, adverse health effects, treatment options, and the recovery process along with guidelines for healthy weight control.
